channel.title: Fight Caves/Jad [PROJECT INSANITY]
channel.description:
On my Exion/Project Insanity server, my jad is not working properly.
When you hit the Fight Caves teleport, it brings you to the minigame, and you enter the cave.
Jad starts attacking you, and once you kill him another jad respawns.
I need to fix it soon.
MSN is anthonydukaj@live.com or simply reply.
Hit me up if you can help.
Thanks, anthonyduka

item.description:

NpcHandler.java

public void handleJadDeath(int i) {
Client c = (Client)Server.playerHandler.players[npcs[i].spawnedBy];
c.getItems().addItem(6570,1);
c.sendMessage(“Congratulations on completing the fight caves minigame!”);
c.getPA().resetTzhaar();
c.waveId = 300;
}
